<p>avg_gain = gains.rolling(window=period).mean()</p>

<p>avg_loss = losses.rolling(window=period).mean()</p>

<p>rs = avg_gain / avg_loss</p>

<p>rsi = 100 - (100 / (1 + rs))</p>
return rsi</li>
</ul>

